{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act13side_level_act13side_05_end","storyGroup":"act13side","storySort":12,"storyDependence":"act13side_level_act13side_05_beg","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"NL-5","storyName":"人言可畏","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"遭到了无胄盟威胁的临光不得不谨慎起来，而目睹了玄铁威势的青金罗伊也坦然了一段关于白金的过去。感染者骑士们已经蓄势待发，他们打算瘫痪整座城市。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act13side/level_act13side_05_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act13side_05","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":10,"next":12,"characters":["莫妮克","罗伊","玛嘉烈","闪灵","耀骑士","夜莺","发言人麦基","发言人马克维茨","砾","电话那头的声音","查丝汀娜","瑟奇亚克","格蕾纳蒂","感染者骑士","艾沃娜","索娜","托兰"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"卡西米尔2 5-2","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7f/Avg_bg_bg_23_G05.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_npc_208_1","focus":"2","id":8},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫妮克","text":"......之前我还奇怪，为什么你们要带着那个路都走不了的萨卡兹。","id":9,"figure":"avg_npc_208_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫妮克","text":"原来如此。","id":10,"figure":"avg_npc_208_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_208_1","focus":"1","id":11},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"呃......莫妮克阁下，我怎么什么都没感觉到......","id":12,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_208_1#5","focus":"2","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫妮克","text":"......那就少说话，少丢脸。","id":14,"figure":["avg_npc_208_1",4]},{"type":"dialog","id":15},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#1$1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":16},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"......无胄盟吗，有何贵干？","id":18,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",0]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"首先，请允许我向耀骑士道歉。","id":20,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"关于今天无胄盟绑架了玛莉娅一事——","id":21,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":22},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"——","id":23,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#3","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":24},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"——喔，别冲动，再说也不是我干的啊。","id":25,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#3","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":26},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"......你们......卑劣的刽子手！","id":27,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#1$1","focus":"1","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"玛莉娅此时应该已经安全回家了，放心，没有后续针对你们的行动，就算有，也会尽量做得......不那么完美。","id":29,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"无胄盟也只是收钱办事，就算我们不想，毕竟上面的人也盯着，你说对吧？","id":30,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_147_shining_1","name2":"avg_npc_209_1","focus":"1","id":31},{"type":"dialogue","name":"闪灵","text":"......你们在袭击感染者。","id":32,"figure":"char_147_shining_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_147_shining_1","name2":"avg_npc_209_1","focus":"2","id":33},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"这也是上面的安排，别怪我们啊。","id":34,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"恶行不因为其缘由而洗刷罪孽。","id":36,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"......说的也是。","id":38,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"所以，我们今天这不是来打声招呼吗......","id":39,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":40},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"我们没什么好聊的，要动手的话，随时奉陪。","id":41,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":42},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"真是咄咄逼人，直说了吧，我们想摆脱商业联合会的控制。","id":43,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"......什么？","id":45,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"今天来，我就是想把这话挑明的。我们是对立的立场，毕竟现在我们还是联合会的人......","id":47,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"但我们是否可以私下签订一份和平协议呢？","id":48,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#5$1","focus":"2","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"耀骑士","text":"......","id":50,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"你，耀骑士，临光家族和那些附庸，以及“罗德岛”。我们希望你们不要影响到我们的计划。","id":52,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"相对的，无胄盟不会妨碍你的夺冠，更不会对和耀骑士相关的人物出手。","id":53,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_179_cgbird_1","name2":"avg_npc_209_1","focus":"1","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜莺","text":"......那些感染者呢？","id":55,"figure":"char_179_cgbird_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_179_cgbird_1","name2":"avg_npc_209_1#2","focus":"2","id":56},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"......遗憾，我们也不能做到所有事情。","id":57,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"char_179_cgbird_1","name2":"avg_npc_209_1","focus":"2","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"感染者对我们而言也算是个威胁，但是请放心，现在的我们也需要那些感染者骑士——","id":59,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#4$1","focus":"2","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"当你们的替罪者？","id":61,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#2","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"......","id":63,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#2","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"这不是我索求的东西，无胄盟。","id":65,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#2","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"——无胄盟是什么？","id":67,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"古时候，为了对抗荒淫无道的骑士贵族，当地的农民和扈从们串通，雇佣了一批身经百战的杀手。","id":68,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"但是他们——全都失手了。","id":69,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"骑士把叛徒通通吊死，悬挂在城堡之上，以儆效尤。领地内的村民怒不敢言，只能忍气吞声，放弃抵抗。","id":70,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"不过后来，有一位弓手主动请缨，当时人们普遍认为弓箭手无法应对库兰塔骑士的速度，并不抱期望......","id":71,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"然而翌日清晨，那位暴虐骑士的家人们醒来后，却看见那位骑士保持着冲锋的姿势，仰面朝天，被一杆长枪钉在了广场地面——","id":72,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"等到人们靠近细看，才发现那并不是一杆长枪，而是一支利箭，由玄铁铸造而成的利箭。","id":73,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"“玄铁”，是历史上第一位无胄盟。","id":75,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#6","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"虽然我对于我们只是被雇来的杀手这点还是有自觉的，不过呢......","id":77,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"有些传说，可不是空穴来风。","id":78,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",5]},{"type":"stopmusic","id":79},{"type":"character","name":"char_147_shining_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":80},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":81},{"type":"dialogue","name":"闪灵","text":"——临光！上面！","id":82,"figure":"char_147_shining_1"},{"type":"dialog","id":83},{"type":"character","id":84},{"type":"text","text":"耀骑士抬起头。","id":85},{"type":"text","text":"路灯暗淡，今夜星光璀璨。","id":86},{"type":"text","text":"而其中一颗流星，闪烁了数下之后，偏离了群星的轨道。","id":87},{"type":"text","text":"直坠大地。","id":88},{"type":"dialog","id":89},{"type":"blocker","a":"0.7","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.02","block":"true","id":90},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_avg_arrowshot","id":91},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0.95","g":"0.95","b":"0.95","fadetime":"0.25","block":"true","id":92},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.6","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"8","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","block":"true","id":93},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$normal02_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_bat_normal02_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":94,"musicid":1},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#4$1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"——箭！？","id":96,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"char_147_shining_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#4$1","focus":"1","id":97},{"type":"dialogue","name":"闪灵","text":"斩断它！","id":98,"figure":"char_147_shining_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_147_shining_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":99},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"明白——！","id":100,"fi