心！","id":123,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",6]},{"type":"move","name":"right","xpos":"-180","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":124},{"type":"playsound","key":"$bodyfalldown2","volume":"0.6","id":125},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":126},{"type":"character","name":"char_147_shining_1","id":127},{"type":"dialogue","name":"闪灵","text":"（临光和我同时出剑......竟然，都没能砍断？）","id":128,"figure":"char_147_shining_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"闪灵","text":"......","id":129,"figure":"char_147_shining_1"},{"type":"delay","time":"0.6","id":130},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#5$1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"......没事吧，二位？","id":132,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"char_179_cgbird_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#5$1","focus":"1","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜莺","text":"没、没事......刚、刚才那是......","id":134,"figure":"char_179_cgbird_1"},{"type":"dialog","id":135},{"type":"character","id":136},{"type":"text","text":"玛嘉烈沉默地望向一旁。","id":137},{"type":"text","text":"漆黑的箭矢，如长矛般的箭矢，没入水泥地面之中，悄无声息。","id":138},{"type":"dialog","id":139},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_npc_208_1","focus":"1","id":140},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"了不起......能反应过来还挡开玄铁一箭的人，我还是头一次见。","id":141,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_npc_208_1#4","focus":"2","id":142},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫妮克","text":"......","id":143,"figure":["avg_npc_208_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","id":144},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"耀骑士的剑术果然了得，那边那位赦罪师，也让人看到了一些别开生面的技巧......幸好箭矢是没有生命的——","id":145,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"——那是灵魂的味道吗？萨卡兹？","id":146,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"你这个医师的剑术和法术......究竟到了什么地步？","id":147,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_147_shining_1","id":148},{"type":"dialogue","name":"闪灵","text":"少说废话......这就是你们所谓的，停战协议吗？","id":149,"figure":"char_147_shining_1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#5","id":150},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"你们心里清楚，这一箭并非冲着取你们的性命去的。否则，那边那位坐着的萨卡兹......已经死了。","id":151,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"char_179_cgbird_1","id":152},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜莺","text":"......","id":153,"figure":"char_179_cgbird_1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","id":154},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"招呼就到此为止，各位，请认真考虑一下我们的提议。","id":155,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_208_1","id":156},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫妮克","text":"......还有，希望刚才那箭能让你们明白，无胄盟并非在向你们求饶——","id":157,"figure":"avg_npc_208_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_208_1#2","id":158},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫妮克","text":"“玄铁”有三位。","id":159,"figure":["avg_npc_208_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_208_1","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫妮克","text":"你们能挡下几箭？","id":161,"figure":"avg_npc_208_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","id":162},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"慢着！","id":164,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",6]},{"type":"dialog","id":165},{"type":"character","id":166},{"type":"text","text":"两位无胄盟的身影溶解在了霓虹与月光的间隙中。","id":167},{"type":"text","text":"耳边只剩下爵士乐的声响。","id":168},{"type":"dialog","id":169},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"......","id":171,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"char_147_shining_1","id":172},{"type":"dialogue","name":"闪灵","text":"......“玄铁”，有着黑曜石般光泽的金属，很重。","id":173,"figure":"char_147_shining_1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"闪灵","text":"就如其名......像是从......天上落下的一般。","id":174,"figure":"char_147_shining_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_147_shining_1","name2":"char_179_cgbird_1","focus":"2","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"夜莺","text":"天......上？","id":176,"figure":"char_179_cgbird_1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"......天上。","id":178,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",6]},{"type":"dialog","id":179},{"type":"character","id":180},{"type":"text","text":"耀骑士再次看向天空。","id":181},{"type":"text","text":"群星在此刻仿佛杀机四伏。","id":182},{"type":"dialog","id":183},{"type":"character","name":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","id":184},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"这支箭......从很远的地方射出，极高的抛物线让它变得仿佛从天而降。","id":185,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"char_147_shining_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":186},{"type":"dialogue","name":"闪灵","text":"这不合常理。","id":187,"figure":"char_147_shining_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_147_shining_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"2","id":188},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"......无胄盟，“玄铁”大位，如那个油嘴滑舌的男人所说，他们才是“无胄盟”一词的原典。","id":189,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",6]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"玛嘉烈","text":"这样的杀手，此刻，也许正盯着我们的项上人头。","id":190,"figure":["avg_1014_nearl2_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"char_147_shining_1","name2":"avg_1014_nearl2_1#7$1","focus":"1","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"闪灵","text":"我们确实得警惕一些。这里是卡西米尔......","id":192,"figure":"char_147_shining_1"},{"type":"character","name":"char_147_shining_1","id":193},{"type":"dialogue","name":"闪灵","text":"是他们罪行的堡垒。","id":194,"figure":"char_147_shining_1"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2.5","id":195},{"type":"dialog","id":196},{"type":"character","id":197},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":198},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/af/Avg_bg_bg_23_G03.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":199},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":200},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta1_180603/m_dia_darkness01_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":201,"musicid":2},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1","name2":"avg_npc_212_1","focus":"2","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人麦基","text":"......马克维茨。","id":203,"figure":"avg_npc_212_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_212_1","focus":"1","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人马克维茨","text":"怎么了吗？麦基先生？","id":205,"figure":["avg_npc_211_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_212_1","focus":"2","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人麦基","text":"......总觉得你这两天变得轻快了许多，发生什么了吗？","id":207,"figure":"avg_npc_212_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1","name2":"avg_npc_212_1","focus":"1","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人马克维茨","text":"不......只是找到了自己该做的事情。","id":209,"figure":"avg_npc_211_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1","name2":"avg_npc_212_1#3","focus":"2","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人麦基","text":"该做的事情吗。","id":211,"figure":["avg_npc_212_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1","name2":"avg_npc_212_1","focus":"2","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人麦基","text":"听说，你和罗德岛制药的关系十分密切，前些日子，还安排了他们的领导人与其他几家企业的会晤？","id":213,"figure":"avg_npc_212_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_212_1","focus":"1","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人马克维茨","text":"是这样没错......怎么了吗？","id":215,"figure":["avg_npc_211_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_212_1#2","focus":"2","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人麦基","text":"你也知道，感染者的舆论压力越来越大，我们总要做出一些反应。","id":217,"figure":["avg_npc_212_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人麦基","text":"罗德岛是零号地块为数不多的境外企业，但也是得到监正会大力支持的企业。","id":218,"figure":["avg_npc_212_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_212_1","focus":"2","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人麦基","text":"我们需要认真对待罗德岛。实际上，今天几位常务董事已经明示，要我们调查......并处理罗德岛。","id":220,"figure":"avg_npc_212_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_212_1","focus":"1","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人马克维茨","text":"处......理吗？","id":222,"figure":["avg_npc_211_1",6]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_212_1","focus":"2","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人麦基","text":"零号地块有一些秘密，是不能让外人知道的。","id":224,"figure":"avg_npc_212_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人麦基","text":"这件事直接动用了无胄盟，“白金”大位的指挥权也会再次让渡给此事的负责人。","id":225,"figure":"avg_npc_212_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_212_1","focus":"1","id":226},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人马克维茨","text":"......连无胄盟都......！？","id":228,"figure":["avg_npc_211_1",2]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_212_1#2","focus":"2","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人麦基","text":"不过......我向董事会提议，把这件事的负责人变更成了你。","id":230,"figure":["avg_npc_212_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1#9","name2":"avg_npc_212_1#2","focus":"1","id":231},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人马克维茨","text":"......！麦基先生！感谢您！","id":233,"figure":["avg_npc_211_1",8]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1#9","name2":"avg_npc_212_1","focus":"2","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人麦基","text":"没什么。","id":235,"figure":"avg_npc_212_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人麦基","text":"只是希望你和罗德岛的私交，能让这件事变得简单一些。在卡西米尔做生意，总得按卡西米尔的规矩来。","id":236,"figure":"avg_npc_212_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1","name2":"avg_npc_212_1","focus":"1","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人马克维茨","text":"我明白。","id":238,"figure":"avg_npc_211_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1","name2":"avg_npc_212_1","focus":"2","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人麦基","text":"......还有一件事。这件事请绝对不要声张，否则会很危险。虽然目前白金及大部分无胄盟还在管控之内。","id":240,"figure":"avg_npc_212_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1","name2":"avg_npc_212_1#4","focus":"2","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人麦基","text":"但无胄盟内部出了问题，大问题。","id":242,"figure":["avg_npc_212_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_211_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_212_1#4","focus":"1","id":243},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.5","xstrength":"15","ystrength":"15","vibrato":"20","randomness":"70","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":244},{"type":"dialogue","name":"发言人马克维茨","text":"......！","id":245,"figure":["avg_npc_211_1",2]},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2.5","id":246},{"type":"dialog","id":247},{"type":"character","id":248},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":249},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/1/12/Avg_bg_bg_23_G09.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":250},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":251},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":252},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":253},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"......博士。","id":254,"figure":"avg_237_gravel_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"您又在发呆了吗？感到无聊吗？","id":255,"figure":"avg_237_gravel_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"最近的大骑士领，有很多人开始抵制感染者骑士......","id":256,"figure":"avg_237_gravel_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#3","id":257},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"如果不是这样的话，嘻......我倒是愿意陪您稍微逛一逛呢。","id":258,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",2]},{"type":"dialog","id":259},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"261","text":"比起我，阿米娅她们承受着更大的压力。"}},"values":[],"id":260},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":261,"end":264},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#6","id":262},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"是这样......当然。","id":263,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"我时常在想，你们这些人，来卡西米尔的目的......究竟是什么呢？","id":264,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",5],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":265},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"267","text":"可露希尔总是抱怨财政赤字，总得想想办法。"}},"values":[],"id":266},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":267,"end":269},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#5","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"......","id":269,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",4],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":270},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"272","text":"临光也说，卡西米尔还有等待被拯救的人们。"}},"values":[],"id":271},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":272},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"274","text":"我问过她，她打算怎么做。"}},"values":[],"id":273},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":274},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"276","text":"得到答案之后，我决定支持她。阿米娅也是。"}},"values":[],"id":275},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":276,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":277},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"279","text":"所以我们来了。"}},"values":[],"id":278},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":279,"end":283},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#4","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"......不算太意外的答案呢。","id":281,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",3]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#5","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"虽然在过去，我只会觉得这是冠冕堂皇的借口......耀骑士在罗德岛的地位很高吗？","id":283,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",4],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":284},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"286","text":"我还真没考虑过“地位”这个问题。"},"2":{"id":"292","text":"我很尊敬临光小姐，与地位无关。"},"3":{"id":"299","text":"玛嘉烈·临光是我们的干员，我并没有把她当做耀骑士。"}},"values":[],"id":285},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":286,"end":290},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"......听说现代的卡西米尔企业也流行鼓吹扁平化管理，但其实只是让底层劳动者放松警惕的由头。","id":288,"figure":"avg_237_gravel_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"不过，如果博士您这么说......我就当是吧。","id":289,"figure":"avg_237_gravel_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"这是不是意味着，如果我也去罗德岛兼职的话，能和您......平起平坐呢？","id":290,"figure":"avg_237_gravel_1#1","end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":291},{"type":"predicate","references":["2"],"id":292,"end":297},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1","id":293},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"欸，真让人羡慕。","id":294,"figure":"avg_237_gravel_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#6","id":295},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"您是排除了身份与地位，单纯将耀骑士作为一个“人”来看待......还尊敬着她吗？","id":296,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",5]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"罗德岛的其他人......会得到您这样的尊敬吗？如果会的话，我倒是有些好奇呢。","id":297,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",5],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":298},{"type":"predicate","references":["3"],"id":299,"end":305},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#6","id":300},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"有很多骑士都尊敬着耀骑士。不过，原因无非两种。","id":301,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#2","id":302},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"要么因为，她是“临光”，要么因为，她是“耀骑士”。","id":303,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1","id":304},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"能听到别的答案，对一个卡西米尔的骑士而言，可真是一件新鲜事。","id":305,"figure":"avg_237_gravel_1#1","end":true},{"type":"useless","references":["1","2","3"],"id":306},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#2","id":307},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"......博士。","id":308,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#6","id":309},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"我是被贩卖到卡西米尔来的，从那时候起，我就被老爷教育，要时刻准备好为他人献身。","id":310,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",5]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1","id":311},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"哪怕此刻，我也会为了您而死哦？嘻嘻。","id":312,"figure":"avg_237_gravel_1#1"},{"type":"dialog","id":313},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"315","text":"因为我是你的护卫目标？"},"2":{"id":"315","text":"因为监正院的命令？"}},"values":[],"id":314},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"id":315,"end":320},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#2","id":316},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"......所谓的征战骑士，就是这么被训练的啊。","id":317,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"所以，耀骑士的行为，在我看来，有些渺茫，有些遥远。","id":318,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#5","id":319},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"您觉得，为他人的理想献身，是一件伟大的事情吗？","id":320,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",4],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":321},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"323","text":"当然。"},"2":{"id":"323","text":"是的。"}},"values":[],"id":322},{"type":"predicate","references":["1","2"],"text":"","id":323,"end":325},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#2","id":324},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"那如果这个人的理想也是为了他人献身，最后，我们又得到了什么呢？","id":325,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",1],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":326},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"328","text":"得到了一片更加美好的大地。"}},"values":[],"id":327},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":328},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"330","text":"哪怕只美好了一丁点。"}},"values":[],"id":329},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":330,"end":333},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#2","id":331},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"......","id":332,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"天真的想法，这可和您在商业联合会面前机敏的表现大不相符......","id":333,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",1],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":334},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"336","text":"对了，砾小姐。"}},"values":[],"id":335},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":336,"end":338},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#6","id":337},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"您请说。","id":338,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",5],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":339},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"341","text":"如果你觉得我不值得你牺牲，就别这么做。"}},"values":[],"id":340},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":341,"end":344},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#4","id":342},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"0.3","xstrength":"30","ystrength":"30","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"false","id":343},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"......怎么可以说这种话，您在质疑我的忠——","id":344,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",3],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":345},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"347","text":"如果你觉得我值得你牺牲，那就为了我们活下去。"}},"values":[],"id":346},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":347,"end":349},{"type":"character","name":"avg_237_gravel_1#2","id":348},{"type":"dialogue","name":"砾","text":"......","id":349,"figure":["avg_237_gravel_1",1],"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":350},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"352","text":"您只是一名优秀的骑士，罗德岛的合伙人。"}},"values":[],"id":351},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":352},{"type":"decision","options":{"1":{"id":"354","text":"您是自由的。"}},"values":[],"id":353},{"type":"predicate","references":["1"],"id":354,"end":355},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"2.5","id":355,"end":true},{"type":"dialog","id":356},{"type":"character","id":357},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":358},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ac/Avg_bg_bg_23_G07.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":359},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":360},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":361,"musicid":3},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_208_1","focus":"1","id":362},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"......","id":363,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_208_1","focus":"2","id":364},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫妮克","text":"你在想什么？","id":365,"figure":"avg_npc_208_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_npc_208_1","focus":"1","id":366},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"不，只是......很久没见过玄铁出手了。","id":367,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_npc_208_1","focus":"2","id":368},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫妮克","text":"上一次是什么时候？","id":369,"figure":"avg_npc_208_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_npc_208_1","focus":"1","id":370},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"......你还没升到青金这个位置......处决上一任白金的时候。","id":371,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"那时候的白金大位是欣特莱雅的师父......差不多这个意思吧。","id":372,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"那天下着雨，下午四点四十七，本来，我正打算出差去一趟别的城市。","id":373,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"那时候的青金只有我一个人，我突然接到电话，说是“白金”叛逃了，要立刻去处理。","id":374,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_npc_208_1#2","focus":"2","id":375},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫妮克","text":"......然后呢，你亲手杀死了你的同事？","id":376,"figure":["avg_npc_208_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_208_1#2","focus":"1","id":377},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"不。如果真那样的话，恐怕我晚上做梦会觉得不安的吧。","id":378,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_npc_208_1#2","focus":"1","id":379},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"其实等我们匆匆赶到现场的时候......哈哈。那是一栋烂尾楼。","id":380,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_208_1#2","focus":"1","id":381},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"整个三楼面目全非，叛徒......被高高地钉在一堵墙上，胸口插着一支玄铁重箭。","id":382,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"从我不太专业的现场勘探技巧来判断......“白金”曾试图逃离那里，却在半空中被那支重箭横穿胸口，钉入了墙壁。","id":383,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"我当时就在那堵墙的下面。那个爱上目标而试图背叛我们的可怜人，就那么被钉在上面。","id":384,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"我就记得，那堵墙很白。他的死状就像是受难者。","id":385,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#2","name2":"avg_npc_208_1#5","focus":"2","id":386},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫妮克","text":"只有见识太少的傻子才会被嚷嚷着自由与理想的家伙骗到。他们根本不理解生存的本质是什么。","id":387,"figure":["avg_npc_208_1",4]},{"type":"dialog","id":388},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_npc_208_1","focus":"-1","id":389},{"type":"playsound","key":"$phonevibration","volume":"0.6","id":390},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"3","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":391},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":392},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.6","id":393},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","id":394},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"是我。","id":395,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#3","id":396},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"唔......他们终于打算行动了？","id":397,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",2]},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","volume":"0.6","id":398},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#3","name2":"avg_npc_208_1","focus":"2","id":399},{"type":"dialogue","name":"莫妮克","text":"......红松骑士团吗。","id":400,"figure":"avg_npc_208_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_npc_208_1","focus":"1","id":401},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"是啊，他们非常谨慎，不过现在......他们终于按捺不住了。","id":402,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"毕竟这两天连抵制感染者的游行都出现了呢......真滑稽啊，我都搞不清谁才是受害者了。","id":403,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"dialog","id":404},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","name2":"avg_npc_208_1","focus":"-1","id":405},{"type":"playsound","key":"$phonevibration","volume":"0.6","id":406},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"5","ystrength":"3","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":407},{"type":"delay","time":"0.5","id":408},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#2","id":409},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"欸，怎么又是电话，真麻烦啊。","id":410,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_transmissionget","volume":"0.6","id":411},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"喂——","id":412,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#5","focus":"-1","id":413},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电话那头的声音","text":"为什么没有按照坐标移动？","id":414,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电话那头的声音","text":"否则，赦罪师和耀骑士没有机会拦下那一箭。","id":415,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#5","id":416},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"......","id":417,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#5","focus":"-1","id":418},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电话那头的声音","text":"你让他们面朝北方，提前看见了我的箭矢。","id":419,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电话那头的声音","text":"否则，至少，那个坐在椅子上的萨卡兹必死无疑。","id":420,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","id":421},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"啊哈哈，不知道您在说什么——就算打哈哈也没用吧。","id":422,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"这是我临时的判断，老板，对于耀骑士这种不撞南墙不回头的人来说，杀掉一个，只会激化她的行为。","id":423,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1","focus":"-1","id":424},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电话那头的声音","text":"若能让耀骑士失去理智，也未尝不可。","id":425,"figure":"avg_npc_209_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#5","id":426},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"这太危险了，老板。原谅我先斩后奏，但我觉得，现在的威胁恰到好处，过犹不及。","id":427,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗伊","text":"相信我，耀骑士不会妨碍您的计划......说起来，我能问问现在事情怎么样了吗？","id":428,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",4]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_209_1#5","focus":"-1","id":429},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电话那头的声音","text":"......董事会很快就会察觉到。但是没关系，等到感染者们让这座城市瘫痪的时候......","id":430,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电话那头的声音","text":"我会亲自解决最后几个接线人。","id":431,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",4]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"电话那头的声音","text":"从今往后，将不再有人，知晓无胄盟高层的真面目。","id":432,"figure":["avg_npc_209_1",4]},{"type":"playsound","key":"$transmission","volume":"0.6","id":433},{"type":"dialog","id":434},{"type":"character","id":435},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":436},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7f/Avg_bg_bg_23_G05.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":437},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":438},{"type":"character","name":"avg_430_fartth_1","id":439},{"type":"dialogue","name":"查丝汀娜","text":"......就位。","id":440,"figure":"avg_430_fartth_1#1"},{"type":"dialog","id":441},{"type":"character","id":442},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":443},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/0/0a/Avg_bg_bg_kxstreet.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":444},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":445},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_103nc_1","id":446},{"type":"dialogue","name":"瑟奇亚克","text":"我听得见。","id":447,"figure":"avg_npc_103nc_1#1"},{"type":"dialog","id":448},{"type":"character","id":449},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":450},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/a/ac/Avg_bg_bg_23_G07.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":451},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":452},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_123","id":453},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格蕾纳蒂","text":"准备就绪。","id":454,"figure":"avg_npc_123#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_221","id":455},{"type":"dialogue","name":"感染者骑士","text":"哦！我们能做到的！","id":456,"figure":"avg_npc_221"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_123","id":457},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格蕾纳蒂","text":"......索娜。恢复备用电源的速度很快，我们不知道他们是不是有改进过的应急措施。","id":458,"figure":"avg_npc_123#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"格蕾纳蒂","text":"千万......千万不要掉以轻心。","id":459,"figure":"avg_npc_123#1"},{"type":"dialog","id":460},{"type":"character","id":461},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":462},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7f/Avg_bg_bg_23_G05.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":463},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":464},{"type":"character","name":"avg_496_wdmane_1","id":465},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾沃娜","text":"哈，那我是要继续闹点大动静了？","id":466,"figure":"avg_496_wdmane_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_220","name2":"avg_496_wdmane_1","focus":"1","id":467},{"type":"dialogue","name":"感染者骑士","text":"走啊，野鬃，把那些无胄盟的脑袋都打烂！","id":468,"figure":"avg_npc_220"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_220","name2":"avg_496_wdmane_1#10","focus":"2","id":469},{"type":"dialogue","name":"艾沃娜","text":"当然，随时可以出发。","id":470,"figure":["avg_496_wdmane_1",9]},{"type":"dialog","id":471},{"type":"character","id":472},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":473},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wiki/images/7/7d/Avg_bg_bg_23_G04.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":474},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":475},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_122#2","id":476},{"type":"dialogue","name":"索娜","text":"......艾沃娜会正面袭击无胄盟的巡逻小队。","id":477,"figure":["avg_npc_122",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"索娜","text":"半小时后，小灰突袭能源区。不出意外的话，监正会的守卫应该会被“撤走”。","id":478,"figure":["avg_npc_122",1]},{"type":"dialogue","name":"索娜","text":"我会潜入联合会大楼，拿走我们需要的，轻轻松松。","id":479,"figure":["avg_npc_122",1]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_122#8","id":480},{"type":"dialogue","name":"索娜","text":"......那么，开始行动。","id":481,"figure":["avg_npc_122",7]},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_122#8","name2":"avg_npc_213_1","focus":"2","id":482},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"......我可以帮你混进大楼。","id":483,"figure":"avg_npc_213_1#1"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"在这之后，我就帮不上你了，而且也要有人确保道路通畅。","id":484,"figure":"avg_npc_213_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_122","name2":"avg_npc_213_1","focus":"1","id":485},{"type":"dialogue","name":"索娜","text":"已经够了，谢啦，托兰。","id":486,"figure":"avg_npc_122#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_122","name2":"avg_npc_213_1","focus":"2","id":487},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"别忘了我对你说的，你们在做的事情，有着超乎你们自己想象的意义。","id":488,"figure":"avg_npc_213_1#1"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_213_1#6","id":489},{"type":"dialogue","name":"托兰","text":"让所有人都见证一下吧，见证一座城市的恸哭。","id":490,"figure":["avg_npc_213_1",5]},{"type":"dialog","id":491},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":492},{"type":"character","id":493},{"type":"image","id":494}],"characters":["莫妮克","罗伊","玛嘉烈","闪灵","耀骑士","夜莺","发言人麦基","发言人马克维茨","砾","电话那头的声音","查丝汀娜","瑟奇亚克","格蕾纳蒂","感染者骑士","艾沃娜","索娜","托兰"]}